{"tid":158241,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（多圖）砌機械木製模型","createTime":"2017-03-16T06:45:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-16T09:24:41.000Z","uid":34147,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9b4667d9449172abb1b7b8a5fed1155c2e172f66","tid":158241,"uid":34147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T06:45:54.000Z","msg":"嗱戴定頭盔先，之前試過app版up圖係側頭貓咗嘅，今次轉咗upload網希望冇事。如果有問題，我會再試用其他網，順手跪求解決辦法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次整呢個係由德國設計、台灣製造、唔洗螺絲個類嘢嘅機械模型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之前第一眼見到已經勁鐘意，奈何砌完唔知擺邊就冇買。咁啱間鋪呢排租約期滿全場特價，一時忍唔住就買咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n淨係睇個盒都知正嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/gu1ikanc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fgu1ikanc&h=2e0ff5b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/3mp5uivj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F3mp5uivj&h=ef5b9df1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n開箱！佢入面得三樣嘢：木製模型部件、砌法說明書，同部件清單<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/dnq2zyr3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fdnq2zyr3&h=fe4c6795&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢啲部件都整得幾靚，上色上得唔會話好死實（因為冇乜藝術天份，所以特別揀個已經上咗色嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/1waiuged\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F1waiuged&h=c31c7ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到咁多碎濕濕嘅「木製碎件」有啲驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/zmuca7o4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fzmuca7o4&h=78b759ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n擺好個壇就準備作法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 砌呢啲模型最重要係一張大枱，千祈唔可以跌落地，大嘅怕佢爛，細嘅怕整唔見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/m0kzpf79\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fm0kzpf79&h=48142601&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8162c1d32776e506571f476742fae9f41ca3b0e","tid":158241,"uid":25148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T06:47:59.000Z","msg":"好似幾有趣"},{"pid":"95e648fd4e0af757b448f55173be20b59a5b8411","tid":158241,"uid":60275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T06:48:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b9c6fe98318f8c731a56de392cf544a6bf4304f","tid":158241,"uid":34147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T07:00:10.000Z","msg":"（測試過後upload直圖都係會伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我試下避開直圖，減少大家變貓機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n呢張就係部件清單，其實都幾清楚下<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/4jawi7nr\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F4jawi7nr&h=a7783ca7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n搵好1-10號部件就正式落手砌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/3jncd9ey\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F3jncd9ey&h=52076f84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n左邊係佢張砌法說明書，其實佢畫得好仔細。但廢事upload哂人哋啲步驟上嚟，淨係揀咗某幾張圖擺上嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一步係砌咗個底座先，砌完已經可以試轉。轉右邊有個手把位，佢中間個軸就會跟住轉。一陣砌埋上面㗎飛船就&hellip;&hellip; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/62t1ifxh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F62t1ifxh&h=4ba48105&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n齒輪位都係木製。台仔今次又做得幾好，初初未鎖實其實係難轉嘅。但之後可以係另一邊鎖實（下面有圖），鎖完就轉得勁順，超出我意料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （原本以為要就住就住轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/mfkcio8u\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fmfkcio8u&h=1931028f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢邊個塊大圈圈就係鎖實中間條軸唔會條條「fing」，因為要「鎖實」，其實好撚難上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成個模型我諗我花最多時間就你上呢兩個圈圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/1k4ptgq8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F1k4ptgq8&h=1773bb08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嚟到呢度有樣嘢值得一讚嘅！<br />\n話說我本身好少砌模型，見到下圖第一直覺就係插落去利用個凹位推前kick實（如下圖）。但咁樣做後面會有虛位核核突突咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/1tafnoyg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F1tafnoyg&h=cf244820&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n研究咗一輪之後（其實只係睇埋下個步驟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），終於發現自己砌錯。正確做法係成個插入去，然後喺個底度有另外一個部件鎖實（如下圖）。咁樣真係靚好多又實好多，德國佬台仔都好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/bv7harqn\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fbv7harqn&h=3a376c11&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d44235226735c393f231bc590cc31d03b55ab92","tid":158241,"uid":32485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T07:02:13.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"8942ead9daaba8bfac04111e52359512d7644099","tid":158241,"uid":42131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T07:03:43.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"83a868f1e9e4b537007f5318ced5980f4f2b9bbd","tid":158241,"uid":13948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T07:05:50.000Z","msg":"lm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09d77e06cb2c940885633363a17e0593c71970b8","tid":158241,"uid":65747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T07:06:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ea9d4c937d408c6ecc69b6a543bb37b36e53536","tid":158241,"uid":34147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T07:23:12.000Z","msg":"（屌你老母出橫圖你同我成張圖調轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點撚樣算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n呢個時候轉佢已經可以見到成枝棍跟住轉，但我唔識upload gif<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一陣再搵，連埋製成品一次過upload<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/gd9u1mfl\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fgd9u1mfl&h=eedbb40e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n砌呢個嘢令我學習咗「執拾」嘅重要性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有啲部件細細舊真係好撚難搵，砌砌下都係決定用少少時間分一分類<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ybjk6hin\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fybjk6hin&h=80988549&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個位又係值得一讚嘅！<br />\n話說砌個陣久唔久就會見到有啲窿，啲啲窿窿其實係預你兩個部件砌埋一齊個陣有位走盞。兩個部件如果緊貼咁樣砌，入面壓力會好大（特別係有啲位佢刻意做到比一般緊，做到「鎖實」嘅效果）。同埋我諗佢個走盞位係預埋冷縮熱脹，都唔會跌出嚟或者撐爆咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：鳩噏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/up7y4jlg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fup7y4jlg&h=7be5a6f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n砌完條友就砌飛船鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 初步成型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/rclofbv3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Frclofbv3&h=e2b203be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n要讚again係佢飛船入面啲色都好靚，唔會話入面睇唔到就求祈交貨一撻啡色扮木紋就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/aw0eckt1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Faw0eckt1&h=5bbbcbc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n俾返個鐘你，即刻靚仔咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/z7mpnj54\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fz7mpnj54&h=07562527&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n題外話，如果有巴絲想戰嘅話提一提你：砌呢啲位個陣，<strong>最好係砌好隻手先成隻手砌上身</strong>。我就係伏咗嘅例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 砌咗上半手之後用唔到力怕整爛成個模型，砌唔到下半手上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/rs1uxy0m\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Frs1uxy0m&h=09ebc927&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dc7966c6a9a52c30fe80ac5d91e9cfe2295281ac","tid":158241,"uid":58666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T07:39:21.000Z","msg":"呢個模型幾得意 之前上網睇過片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打係邊入手?"},{"pid":"d0d4691994831beef2eaa7d428202bfe10acfead","tid":158241,"uid":34147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T07:48:20.000Z","msg":"去到呢度基本上已經成型，加個頂同上面啲轉葉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/04pd6wc7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F04pd6wc7&h=776c66a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似門嘅飛翼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 尾唔知有乜用嘅遮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋最重要嘅螺旋槳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好靚呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/eabmq1gr\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Feabmq1gr&h=bd268757&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後加埋左右嘅雲、水泡、花瓶、尾嘅錨，其實已經砌完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以下直接出細節圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個頭頂兩盞燈仔好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/45xc0wj3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F45xc0wj3&h=78c81509&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雲圖（唔是講套戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）其實影呢張相個陣心諗：「屌你老母我一開始話砌唔到個兩個圈圈到最後都係砌唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好柒」<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/oc27hlf6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Foc27hlf6&h=86888578&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n正面係完全見唔到機師先生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/9oy6rxjc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F9oy6rxjc&h=fe187e49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n右邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/m2qn5zs0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fm2qn5zs0&h=3fa2283f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見到水泡、花瓶同個錨未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/14w2oe65\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F14w2oe65&h=e363a924&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">絕密大公開！！！！</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n機師bb與駕駛艙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/z2aj9q8d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fz2aj9q8d&h=56cedee6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以話我知左邊個舊嘢係做咩嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/k2pimufr\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fk2pimufr&h=b2d86267&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（非打手）如果有巴絲有興趣，下面有盒可以參考下。咁啱撞正間鋪執笠，連埋折買咗$289<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/rbt8k04i\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Frbt8k04i&h=e3995ee5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後問聲：有冇巴絲識upload片<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eca3de6c68abce0d11d1aed248f10e115a5d295f","tid":158241,"uid":34147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T07:50:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">sorry兩張圖調轉咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n個頭頂兩盞燈仔好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/oc27hlf6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Foc27hlf6&h=86888578&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雲圖（唔是講套戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）其實影呢張相個陣心諗：「屌你老母我一開始話砌唔到個兩個圈圈到最後都係砌唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好柒」<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/45xc0wj3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F45xc0wj3&h=78c81509&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07f994b251eba852f52bd0c2ff7dc33da9d3cca0","tid":158241,"uid":34147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T08:26:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個模型幾得意 之前上網睇過片<img src=\"/a